    ('SOAD-S 290', 'PHOTOGRAPHY I', '8518', 'Class Status', 'TuTh Tuesday, Thursday 2:20 PM–5:05 PM', 'FA 004', 'Shanti Knight', 5, NULL, 'Lecture', '3', 'FINE ARTS', ARRAY[]::TEXT[], 'Basic practice of digital camera operation, exposure calculation, exposing, image file management, image optimization and digital printing. Guidance toward establishment of a personal photographic aesthetic. A digital SLR camera is required.', ARRAY['IUB GenEd A&H credit
